{"sn22.31:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 22.31 ","sn22.31:0.2":"3. Bharavagga ","sn22.31:0.3":"Aghamulasutta ","sn22.31:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn22.31:1.2":"“Aghanca, bhikkhave, desessami aghamulanca. ","sn22.31:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn22.31:1.4":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, agham? ","sn22.31:1.5":"Rupam, bhikkhave, agham, vedana agham, sanna agham, sankhara agham, vinnanam agham. ","sn22.31:1.6":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, agham. ","sn22.31:1.7":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, aghamulam? ","sn22.31:1.8":"Yayam tanha ponobhavika nandiragasahagata tatratatrabhinandini; ","sn22.31:1.9":"Seyyathidam—kamatanha, bhavatanha, vibhavatanha. ","sn22.31:1.10":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, aghamulan”ti. ","sn22.31:1.11":"Dasamam. "}